@startuml

start

:Choose pivot element;
:Partition the array around the pivot using standard partition function <font color=red> O(n) </font>;
:If depth limit is reached, switch to heapsort <font color=red> O(n log n) </font>;
:Recursively apply introsort to the left partition <font color=red> T(n/2) </font>;
:Recursively apply introsort to the right partition <font color=red> T(n/2) </font>;
stop

@enduml
